the homestretch is a 2014 american documentary film produced and directed by anne de mare and kirsten kelly .   the film premiered at the 2014 hotdocs film festival on april 26 , 2014 .   it went on to play at the 2014 afi docs film festival and the 2014 human rights watch film festival .   independent lens , the orchard , bull frog films , and java films acquired distribution rights to the film .   independent lens broadcast the film nationally on pbs , while the orchard released it through digital platforms on november 21 , 2014 .